content: Getting this installed as alarm or ringtone took luck and persistence. But the music is wonderful.
Does not work for Samsung S20. I love the music, but instead of changing my ringtones, this app deletes my ringtones. I will be happy to rate higher when it works for the phone I have.
I bought Xperia 1, it worked like charm on Android 9. However when my phone updated to Android 10. The ringtone dont work anymore. Please do something.
Works flawlessly as a ringtone and for the alarm on my Note 8, however, as much as I love this piece, due to it's length, I just can't have it as a notification.
